      "body" : "Use of String constructors without charset parameter is not the best practice from the internationalization point of view. I would suggest <code>new String(Files.readAllBytes(Paths.get(filePath)), StandardCharsets.UTF_8);</code> assuming the file is in UTF-8 encoding, which is true in most cases in these days."
