      "body" : "@KuroKurosaka I don&#39;t mean the literal sequence <code>\\Z</code>, I mean the file may actually contain the &#39;End of string&#39; character somewhere in the middle of the file. It happened to me, and was the reason the accepted answer did not work for me."
    }, {
